<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Langrain's Personal Blog</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 0;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        h1 { margin: 0; color: #2c3e50; }
        .subtitle { color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 1.1em; }
        .post-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .date { color: #999; font-size: 0.9em; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        a { color: #3498db; text-decoration: none; }
        a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 50px; color: #777; font-size: 0.8em; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Hello, I'm Langrain 👋</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Developer | Writer | Tech Enthusiast</p>
    </header>

    <main>
        <!-- Article 1 -->
        <article class="post-card">
            <span class="date">October 24, 2023</span>
            <h2><a href="#">My First Post on GitHub Pages</a></h2>
            <p>Welcome to my personal website! I built this using simple HTML and CSS hosted directly on GitHub. It's fast, free, and easy to maintain.</p>
        </article>

        <!-- Article 2 -->
        <article class="post-card">
            <span class="date">September 15, 2023</span>
            <h2><a href="#">Why I Love Coding</a></h2>
            <p>Coding is like solving a puzzle every day. In this post, I share my journey into software development and the tools I use daily.</p>
        </article>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 Langrain. Built with ❤️ on GitHub.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
